A virtual credit card is a credit card without the physical plastic card. Buyer will get the card number, expiry, and other relevant details. The virtual can be used to make purchases such as online and telephone purchases where a physical plastic card isn't required.

Site was operated by [The Madhatter](http://www.bitcoin.org/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=14) who also operate the [[Bitcoin_4_Cash]] service.  It is no longer in operation.

